Hold CTRL + drag across the pink "bypassed" nodes for rows 2-8 to select them and press CTRL+B to unbypass.

To iterate quickly on the prompts, use CTRL+B to bypass all but the first node group (1-1)

In each "SaveAudio" node, change the word after "MozAIk_" to reflect your choise of prompt.

e.g the SaveAudio filename_prefix "audio/1-1/MozAIk_siren" should be modified to "audio/1-1/MozAIk_160bpm trap heaven church dubstep jungle"

https://huggingface.co/audo/stable-audio-open-1.0/blob/main/model.safetensors

Download stable_audio_open_1.0.safetensors and place in ComfyUI > models > checkpoints folder. 

Download "t5_base.safetensors" from the Model Manager.
